 as a hub so your character can move freely</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.webm?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/f44cd4f652557b8d49b695e570610a97.mp4?t=1769809638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/95ea6192a34380227b2b0653cf48f287.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >it's dangerous to go alone, so there will be companions to help you: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip and upgrade each one as needed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting near them will increase their devotion towards you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High devotion will give small buffs for you and companion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special optional mission for each companion with unique reward</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And tea drinking of course</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/1b1979ebc985512f81de2f3f64ccedaa.poster.avif?t=1769809638\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775320/extras/1b1979ebc985512f81de2f3f64ccedaa.web